{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":8,"day":5}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"海防线上的节日","authors":["邢万生"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”建军节前夕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令员率艇队出海待机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他好象年轻了十岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走路都哼着歌曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别说司令员这般高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士心中都喜上加喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎“四人帮”后第一个“八一”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来，浪花，让我们挽起手臂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锚地的夜景惹人醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令员讲起了南昌起义……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿时，耳边传来暴风雨般的枪声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声里飘展着千百面红旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前又出现了井冈山、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山，毛主席指挥我们走过征途万里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，英明领袖华主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正率领着我们走向新的胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚今追昔情更深呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色信号弹腾空起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司令员下令：编队出击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把战斗的捷报献给统帅华主席！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}